quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,57,"Aw taqoola law anna Allaha hadaneelakuntu mina almuttaqeen"
  39,58,"Aw taqoola heena tara alAAathabalaw anna lee karratan faakoona mina almuhsineen"
  39,59,"Bala qad jaatka ayateefakaththabta biha wastakbarta wakunta minaalkafireen"
  39,60,"Wayawma alqiyamati tara allatheenakathaboo AAala Allahi wujoohuhum muswaddatunalaysa fee jahannama mathwan lilmutakabbireen"
  39,61,"Wayunajjee Allahu allatheenaittaqaw bimafazatihim la yamassuhumu assoo-owala hum yahzanoon"
  39,62,"Allahu khaliqu kulli shay-inwahuwa AAala kulli shay-in wakeel"
  39,63,"Lahu maqaleedu assamawatiwal-ardi wallatheena kafaroo bi-ayatiAllahi ola-ika humu alkhasiroon"
  39,64,"Qul afaghayra Allahi ta/muroonneeaAAbudu ayyuha aljahiloon"
  39,65,"Walaqad oohiya ilayka wa-ilaallatheena min qablika la-in ashrakta layahbatannaAAamaluka walatakoonanna mina alkhasireen"
  39,66,"Bali Allaha faAAbud wakunmina ashshakireen"
  39,67,"Wama qadaroo Allaha haqqaqadrihi wal-ardu jameeAAan qabdatuhu yawmaalqiyamati wassamawatu matwiyyatunbiyameenihi subhanahu wataAAala AAammayushrikoon"
